message.content: The paper most likely belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and information retrieval. Other likely sub-categories include "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), and "cs.CY" (Computers and Society) as the paper also touches upon generalizability of AI methods and techniques, corpus construction, and decision methodology.
